    "tips": [
        "This is the MOST important database to maintain if you are using the ToggleSwitch. Remember to add every skin and the variant you use here so it gets properly switched on and off.",
        "Order matters! The script goes down the list, (de)activating each skin one by one, effectively ignoring any load order values you used in Rainmeter. Bottommost skins first, topmost skins last.",
        "Use backslash (\\) and not forwardslash (\/). Rainmeter automatically escapes the backslash so you don't (and shouldn't) type it twice.",
        "The [Skin] parameter will start its pathfinding from the [Rainmeter\\Skins] folder which by default should be installed in [Documents].",
